{"tid":1783453,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"與楊千嬅開音樂會 Supper Moment願望成真","createTime":"2019-12-14T21:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T02:07:33.000Z","uid":27764,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"046dac4f6cc7006625a3132790142f49e758543c","tid":1783453,"uid":27764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T21:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2019年12月14日<br />\n<br />\n楊千嬅與Supper Moment（SM）昨晚合作舉行MOOV Live音樂會，SM表示自從為千嬅創作歌曲《一二三，三二一》後，一直期待與她同台演出，今次獲撮合願望成真。千嬅坦言非常欣賞SM的作品，特別是他們的勵志抒情歌，所以她選唱《大丈夫》。<br />\n<br />\n開場時，千嬅與SM合唱《懂得快樂》、《Wonder Woman》、《靈感床》及《熱血青年》，為音樂會揭開序幕。之後再送上《勇》、《最後的歌》和《一個人的童話》等經典作品。結尾部分，千嬅與SM由《滾》、《幸福之歌》，一路唱到《全世界暫停》，最後再來唱《What a Wonderful World》。5人合作再加入40人合唱團，令樂迷度過愉快一晚。<br />\n<br />\n(即時娛樂)<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191214/1576337388986/與楊千嬅開音樂會-supper-moment願望成真\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191214%2F1576337388986%2F%E8%88%87%E6%A5%8A%E5%8D%83%E5%AC%85%E9%96%8B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83-supper-moment%E9%A1%98%E6%9C%9B%E6%88%90%E7%9C%9F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=e1597035\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191214%2F1576337388986%2F%E8%88%87%E6%A5%8A%E5%8D%83%E5%AC%85%E9%96%8B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83-supper-moment%E9%A1%98%E6%9C%9B%E6%88%90%E7%9C%9F&h=2c5728b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191214/1576337388986/與楊千嬅開音樂會-supper-moment願望成真</a>"},{"pid":"285a2e60ba09a144e8f4f0e491a2db5492b8f087","tid":1783453,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T21:42:49.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br 